"输入 **产品名称**；在 **自动编程检测类型** 中按需勾选关注的检测项（如 本体、极性、焊点、焊盘沾胶、IC 引脚、文字 "
"等）；如有需要，可在 **自动编程参数** 中开启 **桥接** 检测并设置 **邻近距离（像素）** 阈值。完成后点击 **下一步**。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:-1
#, fuzzy
msgid "创建产品-基本信息"
msgstr "Create Product"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:82
#, fuzzy
msgid "**2. 将 PCB 放置在传送带上**"
msgstr "**Place the PCB on the Conveyor**"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:84
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"选择对应传送带并点击 **锁定传送带**，确认或输入传送带宽度后点击 **进板**，PCB 将自动输送至相机下方的拍摄/定位区域；到位后点击 "
"**下一步**。"
msgstr ""
"Place the PCB flat in the center of the conveyor, select the "
"corresponding conveyor, and click \"Lock\". Enter or confirm the conveyor"
" width parameter, then click \"PCB In\"; the PCB is automatically "
"conveyed to the capture/positioning area beneath the camera. Once in "
"place, click \"Next\"."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:86
msgid "**3. 获取尺寸**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:88
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"若已知 PCB 尺寸，直接输入其宽度与高度（单位：mm）。若尺寸不确定，可移动相机分别拍摄 PCB "
"左下角与右上角，在图像上依次点击这两个位置并选择 **自动计算**，系统将自动推算尺寸。"
msgstr ""
"If the PCB dimensions are known, enter the width and height directly (in "
"mm), then click \"Next\". If the dimensions are uncertain, move the "
"camera to capture the lower-left and upper-right corners of the PCB, "
"click these two positions on the image in turn, and choose **Auto "
"Calculate**; the system will automatically estimate the dimensions."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:90
#, fuzzy
msgid "**4. 拍摄**"
msgstr "**Capture Full PCB**"

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:92
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"点击拍摄，系统将联动相机与传送带分区采集并自动拼接生成完整 PCB "
"图像；随后框选用于自动编程的有效区域（通常为整板；若需排除治具/夹具边缘，可适当收缩）。该基准图像将作为后续自动编程、对齐与检测的参考，务必使用洁净、无缺陷的"
" **Golden board（良品板）** 拍摄。此界面可实时调整相机参数（**曝光时间**、**增益**、**gamma** "
"等）；如效果不佳，可重新拍摄覆盖上一版本。"
msgstr ""
"Click \"Capture\"; the system coordinates the camera and conveyor to "
"capture the board in sections and automatically stitches them into a "
"complete PCB image. Then click \"Define Area\" and frame the valid region"
" used for auto-programming (usually the whole board; shrink it slightly "
"to exclude fixture/jig edges if needed). This reference image serves as "
"the baseline for subsequent auto-programming, alignment, and inspection, "
"so be sure to capture it from a clean, defect-free **Golden board**. "
"Camera parameters (brightness, exposure, gain, white balance, point-cloud"
" filtering, etc.) can be adjusted in real time on this screen; if the "
"result is poor, recapture to overwrite the previous version."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:94
msgid "**5. 添加 CAD（可选）**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:96
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"提供 CAD（``.csv``）文件后，系统可自动读取封装(Package)、丝印/标识、料号(PN)、X/Y "
"坐标与旋转角度，并按封装或料号聚类，使同类元件一次建模、加速训练，同时减少后续人工分组与命名工作。"
msgstr ""
"After you provide a CAD (.csv) file, the system can: - automatically read"
" Package, silkscreen/designator, Part Number (PN), X/Y coordinates, and "
"rotation angle; - cluster components by package or part number so "
"identical components are modeled once, accelerating training; - reduce "
"subsequent manual grouping and naming work."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:98
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"上传 ``.csv`` 文件后点击 "
"**预览表格**，在字段映射界面依次指定：料号(PN)、封装(Package)、X、Y、旋转(°)，（可选）层/板面字段；选择坐标单位（mm 或 "
"mil），确认原点与方向一致，随后点击 **运行自动编程**。若 CAD 与拍摄图像未正确重合，可在对齐界面通过旋转、平移、缩放微调后重新运行。"
msgstr ""
"Steps: 1. Upload the `.csv` file and click \"Preview Table\". 2. In the "
"field-mapping screen, assign in order: Part Number (PN), Package, X, Y, "
"Rotation (°), and (optionally) layer/side fields; if multi-layer data "
"exists, you can filter by layer number or side. 3. Select the coordinate "
"unit (mm or mil) and confirm the origin and orientation are consistent. "
"4. Click \"Run Auto Programming\"."

#: ../../source/introduce/quick_start/index.rst:100
#, fuzzy
msgid "若不提供 CAD，后续自动编程仍可执行；检测质量不受影响，仅失去基于封装/料号的聚类加速，系统将对元件逐一建模。自动编程耗时约 30 秒。"
msgstr ""
"If no CAD is provided, auto-programming can still run; inspection quality"
" is unaffected — only the package/part-number clustering acceleration is "
"lost, and the system models each component individually."

